Yet there are a number of things to improve.
You are in the center of Barcelona
You can get to all places quite fast and a Metro Station is right outside the building.
You can reach a lot of spots easily by feet and a Metro Station is as close as it could be.
You can walk or take the subway to almost any place in Barcelona from this location. It is very central and a two minute walk to Las Ramblas etc.
You got everything you need to have a comfortable stay
You have a great view from the terrace.
You have an incredible view over Barcelona and the everything you need is just a few meters away from the house.

You have to read what is included in the listing since there are items missing other AirBnB's of the same level offer (e.g. no detergent for the washer so we had to buy the smallest we can get but we had to leave it behind since we can not bring it back home).

You might take into consideration that it is not in the central neighborhoods. there is a bus that takes you to Cataluna place (num 24) and a metro station 10 min from the apt. The walk from the metro back to the apt is a steep rise (not that convenient at the end of the day). Otherwise the neighborhood is residential and very quiet. Therefore the soirees and lunch are spent considerably far away.
You should really get a permanent internet line there. Everybody needs internet! So many people before commented already about it. Now it is time to change!
You were very thoughtful to provide us with a food hamper and a bottle of bubble for my birthday and we appreciated all your advise.
You will be fit by the time you leave due to stairs but the advantage is you have a great terrace.
Yours truly Kathie
